            Welcome!
             
            I am currently a Masters student at Clinical Psychology
            and Neuroscience, University of Basel. Understanding human
            behavior and cognitive processes has always been one of the
            main motivators for my education. I am passionate about
            deepening my knowledge in research methodology and learning
            about new methods in psychological research. For more
            information, please refer to my CV.
